<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            background: #f8f8f8;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            Referral Notification
        </div>
        <div class="content">
<p>Hello,</p>

<p>
  Congratulations! 🎉 A new school has successfully registered using your referral.
</p>

<p>
  <strong><%= description %></strong>
</p>

<p>
  Thank you for being a valuable part of our community. We truly appreciate your support!
</p>

<p>
  If you have any questions, feel free to contact us <b>9712872793</b>.
</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
